          "docs": "Get an Account's available spend limits, which is based on the spend limit configured on the Account and the amount already spent over the spend limit's duration. For example, if the Account has a daily spend limit of $1000 configured, and has spent $600 in the last 24 hours, the available spend lim"
        }
