              "data": "{}"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Convert a virtual card into a physical card and manufacture it.\nCustomer must supply relevant fields for physical card creation including `product_id`, `carrier`, `shipping_method`, and `shipping_address`.\nThe card token will be unchanged.  The card's type will be altered to `PHYSICAL`.\nThe card wil"
