          },
          "docs": "Clears an existing authorization, either debit or credit. After this event, the transaction transitions from `PENDING` to `SETTLED` status.\n\nIf `amount` is not set, the full amount of the transaction will be cleared. Transactions that have already cleared, either partially or fully, cannot be cleare"
